data.title: Lawrenceburg, TN
data.meta_description: See contact information for City Council Member Robin Williams.
data.text:
Biography

Robin N. Williams and his wife, Cindy, have one son. Robin feels that Lawrenceburg is a great place to live and is thankful to call Lawrenceburg his home.

Employment

Robin is currently owner of Williams Appraisal Service and provides appraisals for Real Estate and is a Certified Real Estate Appraiser in the State of Tennessee and has almost 30 years of experience in the appraisal field. He was elected to the Lawrenceburg City Council in 2007. Robin is currently serving on the Lawrenceburg Utility Systems Board as the appointed Council Member, which is an appointment by the Mayor.

Community Service

Robin is dedicated to helping make the City of Lawrenceburg a better place to live and work and is also dedicated in trying to provide jobs that would give our children a chance to stay here and work if they choose to do.
